    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-01-04T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-01-04T11:00:00-05:00" n="142"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d142">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/2725a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="2" xml:id="d142fn2">The same, January 4, 11 a.m., to the
                        diplomatic representatives in Argentina (as telegram No. 1), Chile (No. 3),
                        and Peru (No. 2).</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-01-04T11:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 4, 1933—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1. Please report any information you can discreetly obtain regarding position
                    Government is likely to take on request of Neutral Commission of December
                        31<note n="3" xml:id="d142fn3">
                        <ref target="frus1932v05#pg_218">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1932, vol. <hi
                                rend="smallcaps">v</hi>, p. 218</ref>.</note> for information as to
                    steps Government would be willing to take in order to bring about peace between
                    Bolivia and Paraguay.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
